---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Aanmelden op je Chromebook" description="Hoe meld je je aan op je Chromebook op Sint-Victor Alsemberg.">

  <section class="bg-[#07153b] text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Chromebookproject</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Aanmelden op je Chromebook</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg max-w-2xl">Alles wat je nodig hebt om je aan te melden — geen apart wachtwoord nodig.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">

      <!-- Gebruikersnaam -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#07153b]/5 border-b border-gray-100 px-6 py-3 flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="bg-[#07153b] rounded-lg w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b] text-sm">Gebruikersnaam</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 py-5">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Vul je gebruikersnaam in op het aanmeldscherm. Het gedeelte <span class="font-mono text-xs bg-gray-100 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5">@sintvictor.be</span> wordt automatisch aangevuld.</p>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-[#07153b]">voornaamachternaam</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm">@sintvictor.be</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wachtwoord -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-[#07153b]/5 border-b border-gray-100 px-6 py-3 flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="bg-[#07153b] rounded-lg w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b] text-sm">Wachtwoord</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 py-5">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Het wachtwoord van je Chromebook is <strong class="text-[#07153b]">hetzelfde als je Smartschool-wachtwoord</strong>. Je hoeft geen apart wachtwoord te onthouden.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wachtwoord gewijzigd -->
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="bg-yellow-400 rounded-xl w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] mb-1">Wachtwoord gewijzigd?</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-800 leading-relaxed">Als je je wachtwoord in Smartschool wijzigt, wordt dit automatisch gesynchroniseerd met je <span class="font-mono text-xs bg-white border border-yellow-300 rounded px-1 py-0.5">@sintvictor.be</span>-account en je Chromebook. Dit kan tot <strong>2 uur</strong> duren.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Terug -->
      <div class="text-center pt-4">
        <a href="/chromebookproject" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#07153b] font-semibold text-sm hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
          </svg>
          Terug naar Chromebookproject
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
